code: import axios from'axios';export var setPosts=function setPosts(posts){return{type:'SET_POSTS',payload:posts};};export var startSetPosts=function startSetPosts(){return function(dispatch){axios.get('https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts').then(function(response){var posts=response.data;dispatch(setPosts(posts));}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};};
